title: Teach Yourself - A Language Series (Books-Audio)
description:
This is a large number of the "Teach Yourself" language series that have been produced, though it is not complete (close, but no cigar). It contains my best rendition of this collection (Missing Content - Teach Yourself.txt) detailing all of the 'bits' that the 'pieces' are missing.

Please Note - if you have a language, or languages, thus far have not been included, or if you have some of the 'bits' that the 'pieces' are missing, then please add and/or update the materials and release it into the world. Our education, as a whole, should never be lost .. even if there are few reasons the use it.
